title: American Horror Story Cult: Predictions for Episode 8
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: This episode looks great so far

I want ALLY to survive and I kind of hope that OZ will be the one to kill Kai, then I think Ally and Oz will take off and change their identities and start over, and I kind of hope Winter takes over the cult when kai dies.

Please, please, please make a video about if you think twisty will be returning to a future episode, or at leased touch on the subject in another video... I feel everyone has  forgotten about him, but I haven’t.
I hope Oz kills Kai in the finale and I really want Winter to be the only survival of the Cult.
